---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Referenzen">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-swiss-navy text-center mb-8 leading-tight">Unsere Referenzen</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 leading-relaxed font-light">
      Erfolgreiche Projekte und Partnerschaften aus verschiedenen Branchen. Vertrauen Sie auf unsere Erfahrung in der Umsetzung von KI- und IT-Lösungen für Unternehmen in der Schweiz.
    </p>
    
    <!-- Responsive Grid für die Referenzkarten -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Iron-Horse GmbH -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <!-- Kategorie-Tag und Icon -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 px-4 py-3 flex justify-between items-center">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600 bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Webentwicklung</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path>
            <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline>
            <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Inhalt -->
        <div class="p-6 flex-grow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-swiss-navy mb-1">Iron-Horse GmbH</h2>
          <div class="text-sm text-swiss-red font-medium mb-4">Digitaler Neuauftritt</div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Für die Iron-Horse GmbH durften wir den kompletten digitalen Auftritt konzipieren und umsetzen. Dabei wurde eine moderne, responsive Website erstellt und die digitale Markenidentität weiterentwickelt. Das Projekt umfasste:
          </p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Technische Umsetzung der neuen Website</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Design, Struktur & Content</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Einrichtung digitaler Kommunikationskanäle</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- ICT Learnfactory -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <!-- Kategorie-Tag und Icon -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-yellow-50 px-4 py-3 flex justify-between items-center">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-amber-600 bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Ausbildung</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H20v20H6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H20"></path>
            <circle cx="10" cy="8" r="2"></circle>
            <path d="M7 13a2 2 0 1 0 4 0v-1H7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Inhalt -->
        <div class="p-6 flex-grow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-swiss-navy mb-1">ICT Learnfactory</h2>
          <div class="text-sm text-swiss-red font-medium mb-4">Didaktische Modernisierung</div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Im Auftrag der ICT Learnfactory wurden verschiedene Ausbildungsinhalte in IT-Modulen überarbeitet und didaktisch optimiert. Zusätzlich übernahmen wir Lehraufträge in den folgenden Bereichen:
          </p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Serverarchitekturen</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Projektmanagement</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Public Cloud-Technologien</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Diese Zusammenarbeit leistete einen nachhaltigen Beitrag zur Qualität der IT-Ausbildung.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Mittelschul- und Berufsbildungsamt -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <!-- Kategorie-Tag und Icon -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-50 to-green-50 px-4 py-3 flex justify-between items-center">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-600 bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Öffentlicher Sektor</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-emerald-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="m22 16.92-3.6-1.4L10 14.9l-1.3-3.6 3.8-9.8"></path>
            <path d="m8 3.4-3.8 9.8 1.3 3.6h13.1l3.4 1.3"></path>
            <path d="M4.2 13.2 2 19.5"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Inhalt -->
        <div class="p-6 flex-grow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-swiss-navy mb-1">Mittelschul- und Berufsbildungsamt Kanton Bern</h2>
          <div class="text-sm text-swiss-red font-medium mb-4">Prüfungsstelle suissefocus</div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Als zentrale Prüfungsstelle unterstützt suissefocus das Mittelschul- und Berufsbildungsamt bei der Durchführung und Bewertung von individuellen praktischen Arbeiten (IPA) von Informatiklernenden. Unsere Aufgaben umfassen:
          </p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Abnahme und Korrektur der IPA</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Fachgerechte Bewertung gemäß Bildungsstandards</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Förderung des Informatiknachwuchses im Kanton Bern</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Milenyumsoft -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <!-- Kategorie-Tag und Icon -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-50 to-purple-50 px-4 py-3 flex justify-between items-center">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-violet-600 bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full">KI-Integration</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-violet-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2c0 .74-.4 1.39-1 1.73V7h1a7 7 0 0 1 7 7h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1H2a1 1 0 0 1-1-1v-3a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h1a7 7 0 0 1 7-7h1V5.73c-.6-.34-1-.99-1-1.73a2 2 0 0 1 2-2Z"></path>
            <path d="M7 10a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v4h2v-4a1 1 0 0 0-1-1Z"></path>
            <path d="M17 10a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v4h2v-4a1 1 0 0 0-1-1Z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Inhalt -->
        <div class="p-6 flex-grow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-swiss-navy mb-1">Milenyumsoft</h2>
          <div class="text-sm text-swiss-red font-medium mb-4">KI-Pilotprojekt mit Coremlis</div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Für Milenyumsoft haben wir ein Pilotprojekt rund um unsere MLOps-Plattform Coremlis gestartet. Ziel war es, Coremlis nahtlos in die bestehende IT-Umgebung zu integrieren und erste KI-Workflows zu etablieren.
            Leistungen:
          </p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Technische Integration</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Testbetrieb mit ausgewählten Daten</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Beratung zur zukünftigen KI-Nutzung</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- DuoIT -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <!-- Kategorie-Tag und Icon -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-rose-50 px-4 py-3 flex justify-between items-center">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-red-600 bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Service Management</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 20a8 8 0 1 0 0-16 8 8 0 0 0 0 16Z"></path>
            <path d="M12 14a2 2 0 1 0 0-4 2 2 0 0 0 0 4Z"></path>
            <path d="M12 2v2"></path>
            <path d="M12 22v-2"></path>
            <path d="m17 20.66-1-1.73"></path>
            <path d="M11 10.27 7 3.34"></path>
            <path d="m20.66 17-1.73-1"></path>
            <path d="m3.34 7 1.73 1"></path>
            <path d="M14 12h8"></path>
            <path d="M2 12h2"></path>
            <path d="m20.66 7-1.73 1"></path>
            <path d="m3.34 17 1.73-1"></path>
            <path d="m17 3.34-1 1.73"></path>
            <path d="m7 20.66 1-1.73"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Inhalt -->
        <div class="p-6 flex-grow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-swiss-navy mb-1">DuoIT</h2>
          <div class="text-sm text-swiss-red font-medium mb-4">ITIL-basiertes Service Management</div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            DuoIT wurde von uns im Bereich Service Management umfassend beraten. Gemeinsam haben wir ein ITIL-konformes Service Management Framework entwickelt und erfolgreich eingeführt. Der Fokus lag auf:
          </p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Aufbau einer strukturierten Service-Organisation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Einführung von ITIL Practices</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-swiss-navy mr-2 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
                <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Schulung der Mitarbeitenden im laufenden Betrieb</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Leichte Hover-Animation für die Karten */
  .hover\:shadow-xl {
    box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
</style> 